The paper deals with evasion attacks on deep learning-based anomaly detectors in industrial control systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves the use of deep learning algorithms (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE) and physical process models (cs.SY).
